3:T63e,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is commission agent software for mandi?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Commission agent software is a purpose-built tool for mandi commission agents (arhtiyas) that automates commission calculation, market fees, hamali and palledari, and maintains a real-time khata for every farmer and buyer."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does MandiGrow calculate commission automatically?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"You configure your commission rate per party or per item once. After that, every sale you record auto-calculates commission, market fees and hamali — and posts the entries to the right ledger instantly. No manual journal vouchers."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I settle multiple farmers at once?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. MandiGrow lets you select multiple farmer parties and run a one-click batch settlement, generating a single payable list with all balances in one screen."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is MandiGrow good for arhtiyas?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes — MandiGrow is the most popular arhtiya software in India. It is built around the way commission agents work at the mandi: gate entry, lot, auction, sale, commission, settlement, payout."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does it generate commission statements?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Generate party-wise commission statements for any date range in one click, in Hindi or English, ready to print or share on WhatsApp."}}]}0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","main",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#f7fbf3] text-gray-900 pt-20","children":[["$","$L2",null,{}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$3"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemLi